## Week 9 {.unnumbered}

### 9-1 How much tropical rain forest have we lost? {.unnumbered}

\vspace{0.3cm}

> *Goal: To use forest cover data to estimate rates of tropical forest loss over time*

1.  ***Read:*** Manuela Andreoni 2023 "Despite Global Pledges, Tree Loss Is Up Sharply in Tropical Forests" [[read online](https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/27/climate/trees-tropical-forests-deforestation.html), 10 min read]

